section_summary: The text appears to be a transcript or summary of a meeting or session. It mentions the opening of the seventeenth session and the importance of cooperation between the council and the government for the benefit of the Kuwaiti people. It also mentions two candidates, Dr. Mohammed Hadi Al-Huwaila and Dr. Falah Al-Hajri. The text concludes with a reference to the legislative session and the date of June 20, 2023.
